high_descs: Turn left to face the wall, walk to the door on the right across the room, and turn right to reach the wooden desk.
Pick up the clock from the back left corner of the desk.
Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the small wooden dresser near the window.
Turn on the small lamp on the right side of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Examine a clock by the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock on the top shelf.
Turn right and walk ahead to the night stand with the lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp on the night stand.
anns.task_desc: Look at an alarm clock by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Back up, turn left, turn right, walk to door, turn right to face desk.
Pick up the clock from top level of desk.
Turn right, cross room to wall, turn left, walk to nightstand.
Turn on the lamp on the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Look at a clock under a lamp.
